metadata.name: MOONWARS - THORIS NNAR by Bart Sears
metadata.description: THORIS NNAR - Illustrated by comic book icon Bart Sears with colors by Carlos D Moreno, exclusively for Comic Boxel’s MOONWARS series NFT releases. These blockchain space barbarians are someone you want on your side in the ongoing Moonwars saga. Many wonder where these warriors came from, and what their agenda is, but no one who dared to ask has ever lived long enough to tell the tale.
